    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst everything is cooking, peel and grate your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>mayo </strong>and<strong> grated garlic </strong>(not a big garlic fan? Try using less!) in a bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and a splash of <strong>cold water </strong>– this is your <strong>garlic mayo</strong></p>",
